Contracts register for schools and colleges
Use the Department for Education’s (DfE) contracts register template and guidance to help you accurately record your school or college’s digital technology contracts.

This contracts register covers digital technology contracts. You may already have a contracts register in place which covers things like buildings, catering, and grounds maintenance. This register is not meant to replace any registers you already have. If you already have a contracts register, you could combine them into one if that’s easier for you to manage. However, you may decide to keep them separate if that works better for your school or college.
